
***** if condition *****

token(s):
IF    if
ELSE  else

rule(s):
1. commande -> IF expr instr_block
2. commande -> IF expr instr_block ELSE instr_block

Description:
conditional expressions.


Example(s):

 if i>10 { print i; }

 if i>10 { print "i>10\n"; } else { print "i<=10"; }


